metadata.name: Under Water
metadata.description:
How do you feel when you’re a few feets under water?

As I sink deeper, I feel breathless

Unable to shout and pass out gas

It doesn’t matter anyway because the water would always find a way to attack me

I would be totally overwhelmed if I let it beat me

But the more I fight, the faster I sink into the water depths.

What do you feel when you’re underwater?
